DATA HANDLING AND PRIVACY

This application accesses media files stored in the WhatsApp status directory
on the local device file system. All operations are performed locally.  No user
data is collected, transmitted, or stored on external servers.

The application requires file system permissions to: 
- Read WhatsApp status files from local storage
- Save status files to the device Documents folder
- Delete saved status files

